## Root cause

I believe this is caused by the same root cause as https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/issues/40803 - we check this setting via the cluster state:
https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/9c6231fd223b42da77e7b979ff8b0a0962a9aab6/x-pack/plugin/watcher/src/main/java/org/elasticsearch/xpack/watcher/support/WatcherIndexTemplateRegistry.java#L156
But since `xpack.ilm.enabled` can only be set via `elasticsearch.yml`, reading it from the cluster state will always result in the default value - it must be read from the `Settings` object created from `elasticsearch.yml` at startup.

